description: Foreigners from Eastern Europe often come to the Czech Republic looking for work. This exotic looking cutie was from Croatia. He wanted to be a musician but soon he realized he would never make enough money by doing that. So he moved here and I was supposed to find him a job. I could see he was pretty well-built, very nicely dressed, the neck tattoo added a nice bad boy touch. A perfect combination of a sweet angel and a thuggish badass. When he mentioned swimming and playing football, I was convinced. The job was his. If he could pay the fee. I was barely able to hide my excitement when he agreed to my dirty offer. Watching him undress was even better than unwrapping a christmas present. I couldn´t wait to lay my hands on him.
title: Dirty Scout 34
